snippet.title: Ratatan - Official Gameplay Trailer | ID@Xbox
snippet.description:
Here's your look at gameplay from Ratatan in this latest trailer for the upcoming rhythm roguelike action game that combines rhythm games and side-scrolling action, with online co-op gameplay supporting up to 4 players. Watch as battles unfold against a giant crab boss and more in the new Ratatan trailer for this game from the creators behind Patapon. In Ratatan, an intense battle unfolds with over 100 characters fighting in a massive melee. 

Ratatan will be available in 2025.

#IGN #Gaming
